      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OLLIE DEEDS (6) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.71 beating INGA AMY. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can continue the winning form. DIVA'S ROSE (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (22.91) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and five minor placings to her credit. Can measure up this time. LARNI LOU (4) showed strong pace early from the inside rail and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing fifth over 410m Horsham in 23.87. Should be in this for a long way. INGA AMY (8) returns here as an each-way chance.",
